WEBVTT

00:00:29.832 --> 00:00:31.229
several times a year

00:00:31.253 --> 00:00:33.717
to visit Sian Ka'an,
to the country of my birth,

00:00:33.741 --> 00:00:35.201
to work with this trash.

00:00:35.225 --> 00:00:36.383
And so far,

00:00:36.407 --> 00:00:40.829
we've documented garbage from
58 different countries and territories

00:00:40.853 --> 00:00:42.430
on six continents,

00:00:42.454 --> 00:00:46.339
all washing ashore
in this paradise in Mexico.

00:00:46.363 --> 00:00:48.977
Although I can never know
where a product was dropped,

00:00:49.001 --> 00:00:52.958
I can, at times, based on the label,
know where something was made.

00:00:52.982 --> 00:00:56.878
In red, you see all of the countries
represented by their trash

00:00:56.902 --> 00:00:58.254
in Sian Ka'an.

00:00:59.650 --> 00:01:03.603
Such as these Haitian butter containers
in all shapes and sizes,